<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>EMA614_10_su_0008_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema614_10.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema614_10_su_0008">
    <div class="scroll_page">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-type="1" data-text="자기주도 4">
            <span class="blue line" lang="y">확인하고 정리해요</span>
            <span lang="y">공부한 내용을 확인해요</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="title type2 jgjd_4_sub_title">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <div class="title_row">
            <span class="nemo_blank"></span>
            <span lang="y">안에 알맞은 말이나 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="scroll_area">
        <div class="question_box">
          <div class="col col1">
            <span lang="y" class="tit">비</span>
            <p lang="y" class="txt1">
              한 양을 기준으로 다른 양이 <br>
              몇 배가 되는지 비교하기 위해 <br>
              기호 :을 사용하여 나타낸 것​
            </p>
            <div class="txt2">
              <span class="num">2 : 5</span>
              <span lang="y" class="txt">비교하는 양</span>
              <span class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="기준량"></math-field>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div> 
          <div class="col col2">
            <span lang="y" class="tit">비율</span>
            <p lang="y" class="txt1">
              기준량에 대한 비교하는 양의 크기​ 
            </p>
            <div class="txt2">
              <span class="num arr">2 : 5</span>
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span class="input_wrap answer2">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                </span>
                <span>5</span>
              </span>
              <span class="num">=0.4</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col col3">
            <span lang="y" class="tit">백분율</span>
            <p lang="y" class="txt1">
              기준량을&nbsp;
              <span class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="100"></math-field>
              </span>
              (으)로 할 때의 비율
            </p>
            <div class="txt3">
                <div class="txt3_col">
                  <span class="label" lang="y">쓰기</span>
                  <span class="txt2" lang="y">40 ％</span>
                </div>
                <div class="txt3_col">
                  <span class="label" lang="y">읽기</span>
                  <span class="txt2" lang="y">40 퍼센트</span>
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area relative">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        
      </div>
      
      </section>
    </div>    
  </div>
</body>

</html>